    <item>
      <title>北京成为最后一个放宽住房规定的中国特大城市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/beijing-becomes-last-mega-china-city-to-ease-housing-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国首都北京放宽了购房首付和抵押贷款的要求，加入中国其他特大城市的行列，支持房地产行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/beijing-becomes-last-mega-china-city-to-ease-housing-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:45:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平前参谋长获委任推动科技突破</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/xi-s-former-chief-of-staff-tapped-to-push-for-tech-breakthroughs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中美在尖端芯片和人工智能领域的紧张局势加剧，国家主席习近平任命其前参谋长带头推动中国在核心技术领域的突破。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/xi-s-former-chief-of-staff-tapped-to-push-for-tech-breakthroughs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:42:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>帕内塔称欧洲央行必须做好应对任何政治冲击的准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/panetta-says-ecb-must-be-ready-to-handle-any-political-shocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员法比奥·帕内塔表示，欧洲央行政策制定者必须做好准备，应对不确定性加剧导致的政治冲击带来的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/panetta-says-ecb-must-be-ready-to-handle-any-political-shocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:09:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿桑奇抵达澳大利亚，认罪后结束流亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/assange-lands-back-in-australia-ending-exile-after-guilty-plea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朱利安·阿桑奇 (Julian Assange) 十多年来首次抵达澳大利亚，此前他在英国监狱服刑并躲藏在厄瓜多尔大使馆后，向美国法庭认罪，并获准以自由人身份返回祖国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/assange-lands-back-in-australia-ending-exile-after-guilty-plea</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 09:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国严厉打击美化恐怖主义行为的外国人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/germany-cracks-down-on-foreigners-who-glorify-terrorist-acts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国执政联盟正寻求通过最新立法严厉打击美化杀害以色列平民或类似恐怖行为的外国人，以便将他们驱逐出境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/germany-cracks-down-on-foreigners-who-glorify-terrorist-acts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 07:53:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国脱欧后，欧洲求职者纷纷放弃英国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/uk-jobs-european-workers-shun-uk-after-brexit-stokes-immigration-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个世纪以来，爱尔兰工人一直短途前往英国寻找工作，以逃避饥荒以及最近的金融危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/uk-jobs-european-workers-shun-uk-after-brexit-stokes-immigration-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉蒂默在受加沙战争影响的纽约初选中击败鲍曼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/latimer-defeats-bowman-in-record-setting-ny-primary-shaped-by-gaza-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔治·拉蒂默在美国历史上最昂贵的国会初选当中击败了纽约州众议员贾马尔·鲍曼，这场竞选暴露了民主党内部在以色列与哈马斯战争问题上的严重分歧。]]></description>
